OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FTV's Julie Goodyear reveals
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fdementia diagnosis         
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Julie Goodyear, known for playing Bet  
OL,6, Lynch in Coronation Street, has        
OL,7, received a "heartbreaking diagnosis" of
OL,8, dementia, her husband has said.        
OL,10,FThe actress had sought medical advice  
OL,11,Fafter "suffering forgetfulness" but    
OL,12,Fthere was now "no hope of a reversal in
OL,13,Fthe situation", Scott Brand said.      
OL,15,FGoodyear, 81, played the               
OL,16,Fleopard-skin-loving barmaid from 1966  
OL,17,Fto 2003.                               
OL,19,F"My darling wife and I have had to come
OL,20,Fto terms with this heartbreaking       
OL,21,Fdiagnosis," Mr Brand said.             
